Partick Thistle have signed Belgian central defender Frederic Frans on a short-term contract. Partick Thistle recruit defender Frederic Frans  Partick Thistle have signed Belgian central defender Frederic Frans on a short-term contract. 
 The 25-year-old former Lierse player, capped at Under-20 level, has agreed a deal until January. 
 &quot;It gives us some extra strength and depth in an area where we were probably still a bit light,&quot; manager Alan Archibald told the club website.&nbsp; 
 &quot;He has experience playing in Belgium's top flight so clearly comes with a bit of pedigree.&quot; 
 Frans, who spent 10 days training with the Glasgow side, could feature in Saturday's squad for the trip to Dundee United. 
 